These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, tea, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, martial-arts, satire
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bus, ship
1. the person driving the airplane is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
6. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person driving the boat is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the ship is between the person watching satire movies and the person drinking 7up##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage         | coffee      | 7up | tea | hot-chocolate |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | crime  | drama   | satire    |
| Transport     | airplane     | bus    | ship    | boat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, horror, scientific, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: american, japanese, mexican, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, boat, jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
2. the person watching epic movies is the mexican##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the japanese##1
7. the american is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching horror movies##2
8. the polish is between the japanese and the person watching scientific movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | epic | scientific   | horror | western  |
| Nationality   | mexican     | american | polish  | japanese |
| Transport     | taxi        | jet-ski  | boat    | airplane |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, kiwi, lemon, tomato
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, purple, lilac, blood-red
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, roller, snowmobile, train
1. the person who likes blood-red is between the person eating grapefruit and the person eating tomato##2
2. the person who likes purple is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating lemon##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
5. the person eating tomato is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes lilac is between the person eating kiwi and the person who likes amber##2
7. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | grapefruit | kiwi   | tomato     | lemon     |
| Color   | purple  | blood-red | lilac   | amber  |
| Transport     | train      | roller | snowmobile | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, horror, romance
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, punk, salsa, soul
House: art-deco, cape-cod, palace, ranch-style
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the person watching disaster movies is the cape-cod house##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
5. the fan of soul is the art-deco house##1
6. the person watching horror movies is the fan of pop##1
7. the fan of salsa is the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | romance   | horror     | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul      | pop        | punk     |
| House         | palace | art-deco | ranch-style | cape-cod   |

