.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, tennis, ice-hockey, snowboarding
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, musical, romance, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, dubstep, jazz, r&b
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the fan of d&b is between the person watching western movies and the fan of r&b##2
6. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Sport          | ice-hockey    | tennis  | snowboarding  | baseball |
| Movie-Genre   | western | musical | action | romance |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | d&b     | r&b    | dubstep |

