.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
4 different games are played: whist, bridge, canasta, monopoly
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, indian, indonesian, japanese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, golf, handball, lacrosse
1. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
2. the person playing bridge is between the person playing monopoly and the person who's sport is cycling##2
3. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the japanese is between the person who's sport is cycling and the australian##2
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the indian is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Game         | whist    | canasta | bridge  | monopoly  |
| Nationality   | indonesian | indian       | japanese | australian |
| Sport         | handball   | cycling      | lacrosse | golf       |

