4. the person who's hobby is reading is the lawyer##1
5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the journalist is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the project-manager##1
8. the person playing whist is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | skydiving | reading   | cooking    | magic-tricks    |
| Job           | teacher   | lawyer    | journalist | project-manager |
| Game   | whist    | mah-jongg | poker    | billiard         |

